ial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14pt;\">　　<img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/1095329/201703/1095329-20170328192456889-1267494879.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 16px; max-width: 900px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(88, 111, 118); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\">　　按照第四步方法或者</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(88, 111, 118); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\">　　ubuntu下</p><div class=\"cnblogs_code\" style=\"margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); overflow: auto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(136, 136, 136) 1px 1px 1px; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250) !important; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important;\"><pre style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important;\">apt-<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;\">get</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5 !important;\"> install openssl\napt</span>-<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5 !important;\">get</span> install libssl-dev</pre></div><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(88, 111, 118); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\">　　centos下</p><div class=\"cnblogs_code\" style=\"margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); overflow: auto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(136, 136, 136) 1px 1px 1px; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250) !important; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important;\"><pre style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important;\">yum -y install openssl openssl-devel</pre></div><h2 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(96, 73, 124); border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(53, 86, 129, 0.3); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px -1px 5px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">六、启动nginx</strong></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(88, 111, 118); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">　　</strong>因为可能apeache占用80端口，apeache端口尽量不要修改，我们选择修改nginx端口。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(88, 111, 118); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\">　　linux 修改路径/usr/local/nginx/conf/nginx.conf，Windows 下 安装目录\\conf\\nginx.conf。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(88, 111, 118); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\">　　修改端口为8090，localhost修改为你服务器ip地址。（成功就在眼前！！）</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(88, 111, 118); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\">　　<img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/1095329/201703/1095329-20170328193900029-2024017752.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 16px; max-width: 900px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(88, 111, 118); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\">　　<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">启动nginx</strong></p><div class=\"cnblogs_code\" style=\"margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); overflow: auto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(136, 136, 136) 1px 1px 1px; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250) !important; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important;\"><pre style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important;\">netstat -ano|grep <span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(128, 0, 128); line-height: 1.5 !important;\">80</span></pre></div><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(88, 111, 118); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\">　　如果查不到执行结果，则忽略上一步（ubuntu下必须用sudo启动，不然只能在前台运行）</p><div class=\"cnblogs_code\" style=\"margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); overflow: auto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(136, 136, 136) 1px 1px 1px; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250) !important; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important;\"><pre style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important;\">sudo /usr/local/nginx/nginx</pre></div><h2 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(96, 73, 124); border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(53, 86, 129, 0.3); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px -1px 5px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">七、nginx重启、关闭、启动</strong></h2><div class=\"Blog_tit4 Blog_tit5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(88, 111, 118); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\"><h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(52, 96, 147); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px -1px 5px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px;\">启动</span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;启动代码格式：nginx安装目录地址 -c nginx配置文件地址</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">例如：</p><div class=\"cnblogs_code\" style=\"margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250) !important; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); overflow: auto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(136, 136, 136) 1px 1px 1px;\"><pre style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important;\">[root@LinuxServer sbin]# <strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">/usr/local/nginx/sbin/nginx -c /usr/local/nginx/conf/nginx.conf</strong></pre></div><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(96, 73, 124); border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(53, 86, 129, 0.3); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px -1px 5px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">停止</span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;nginx的停止有三种方式：</p><ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: disc;\"><h2 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(96, 73, 124); border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(53, 86, 129, 0.3); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px -1px 5px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">从容停止</span></h2></li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">　　1、查看进程号</p><div class=\"cnblogs_code\" style=\"margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250) !important; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); overflow: auto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(136, 136, 136) 1px 1px 1px;\"><pre style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important;\">[root@LinuxServer ~]# ps -ef|grep nginx</pre></div><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/848552/201601/848552-20160102182744854-1291053517.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 16px; max-width: 900px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">　　2、杀死进程</p><div class=\"cnblogs_code\" style=\"margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250) !important; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); overflow: auto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(136, 136, 136) 1px 1px 1px;\"><pre style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important;\">[root@LinuxServer ~]# kill -QUIT 2072</pre></div><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/848552/201601/848552-20160102182652354-960281274.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 16px; max-width: 900px;\"></p><ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: disc;\"><h2 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(96, 73, 124); border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(53, 86, 129, 0.3); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px -1px 5px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">快速停止</span></h2></li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">1、查看进程号</p><div class=\"cnblogs_code\" style=\"margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250) !important; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); overflow: auto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(136, 136, 136) 1px 1px 1px;\"><pre style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important;\">[root@LinuxServer ~]# ps -ef|grep nginx</pre></div><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/848552/201601/848552-20160102183103651-1859453208.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 16px; max-width: 900px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">2、杀死进程</p><div class=\"cnblogs_code\" style=\"margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250) !important; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); overflow: auto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(136, 136, 136) 1px 1px 1px;\"><pre style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important;\">[root@LinuxServer ~]# kill -TERM 2132</pre><pre style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important;\">或 [root@LinuxServer ~]# kill -INT 2132</pre></div><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/848552/201601/848552-20160102183340010-2024212451.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 16px; max-width: 900px;\"></p><ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: disc;\"><h2 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(96, 73, 124); border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(53, 86, 129, 0.3); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px -1px 5px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">强制停止</span></h2></li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</p><div class=\"cnblogs_code\" style=\"margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250) !important; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); overflow: auto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(136, 136, 136) 1px 1px 1px;\"><pre style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot; !important; font-size: 12px !important;\">[root@LinuxServer ~]# pkill -9 nginx</pre></div><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(96, 73, 124); border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(53, 86, 129, 0.3); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px -1px 5px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">重启</span></h2><h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(52, 96, 147); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px -1px 5px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">1、验证nginx配置文件是否正确</span></h3><h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(120, 148, 58); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px -1px 5px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">方法一：进入nginx安装目录sbin下，输入命令./nginx -t</span></h4><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">看到如下显示nginx.conf syntax is ok</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">nginx.conf test is successful</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">说明配置文件正确！</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/848552/201601/848552-20160102184633432-1268782338.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 16px; max-width: 900px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</p><h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(120, 148, 58); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px -1px 5px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">方法二：在启动命令-c前加-t</span></h4><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/848552/201601/848552-20160102185023385-456612180.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 16px; max-width: 900px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(52, 96, 147); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px -1px 5px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;2、重启Nginx服务</span></h3><h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(120, 148, 58); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px -1px 5px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;方法一：进入nginx可执行目录sbin下，输入命令<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">./nginx -s reload&nbsp;</strong>即可</span></h4><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/848552/201601/848552-20160102185521057-1341380905.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 16px; max-width: 900px;\"></p><h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(120, 148, 58); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px -1px 5px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">方法二：查找当前nginx进程号，然后输入命令：kill -HUP 进程号 实现重启nginx服务</span></h4><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/848552/201601/848552-20160102185838167-234856506.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 16px; max-width: 900px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</p></div><h2 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(96, 73, 124); border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(53, 86, 129, 0.3); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px -1px 5px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">八、最终结果<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">：</span></strong></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(88, 111, 118); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\">&nbsp;　<img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/1095329/201703/1095329-20170328194259092-985697133.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 16px; max-width: 900px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(88, 111, 118); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(96, 73, 124); border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(53, 86, 129, 0.3); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px -1px 5px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\">九、项目文件存放路径</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(88, 111, 118); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\">　　放到这个文件下，创建文件夹放入就好。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(88, 111, 118); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 244, 230);\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/1095329/201704/1095329-20170411110107001-2127926117.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 16px; max-width: 900px;\"></p>', 'linux,nginx', '1', '3', '0', '27856cd9-c850-496e-a173-dc1047ec3a48.png', '0', '1', '2020-01-20 14:35:40', '2020-01-20 18:05:51');
